{"tid":2024694,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"越軍展示俄羅斯T-90「紅眼」系統 , 支媒大酸眼紅罵做show","createTime":"2020-05-19T19:15:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T21:28:11.000Z","uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f048f3a417bf57ef7792ffd539ac1a8487c902d7","tid":2024694,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T19:15:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/05/18/phpeWyzP0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F05%2F18%2FphpeWyzP0.png&h=7bdd7c81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n越南陸軍日前大動作展示了從俄羅斯購買的新款T-90S／SK主戰車（SK為指揮車型），以及其配備的Shtora-1主動防禦系統，此系統包含2具位於砲塔正面的紅外線干擾器，看上去如同一雙「紅眼」般，在越南與中國因南海關係緊張時，此舉頗具深意。對此，中國官媒強硬回擊，譏笑越軍作秀，無非是沒嘗過中國紅箭-8反戰車飛彈的厲害。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，越南國防電視台（QPVN）5月12日報導了T-90S／SK主戰車，並展示其配備的Shtora-1主動防禦系統。這款戰車是越南從俄羅斯採購，以取代越軍老舊的中國製T-59戰車，採購數量為64輛，已在去年2月全數運抵越南，配給陸軍最精銳的第201裝甲旅。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，T-90S／SK主戰車配有Shtora-1主動防禦系統，用以防禦雷射、紅外線導引飛彈和干擾目獲系統，包含2具TShU1-7 EOCMDAS紅外線干擾器、4具被動雷射警報器，以及2具3D6煙霧彈發射器，並由同一台電腦來自動控制。該系統可以發射模擬訊號，干擾許多反戰車武器的線性瞄準系統，使其無法命中目標，報導特別指出，對象包含中國的紅箭-8反戰車飛彈。<br />\n<br />\n對此，中國官媒《環球時報》刊出一篇報導，指出Shtora-1系統其實相當不可靠，不過是俄羅斯戰車製造商自吹自擂而已，實際干擾效果沒有這麼出色，敘利亞政府軍的T-90也裝備上Shtora-1系統，但依然無法防禦美製的拖式2A飛彈（TOW 2A）。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，Shtora-1系統還有兩大問題，大功率的紅外線干擾器等於向敵方主動暴露自己位置，而且占了正面裝甲很大的面積，形成防護破口，因此俄羅斯在T-90 MS版本上就已取消這雙「紅眼」。報導稱，越南陸軍此次作秀，無非是沒嘗過中國紅箭-8反戰車飛彈的厲害而已。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://qph.fs.quoracdn.net/main-qimg-2ead6eaace8704c62aaa7ce0372875c3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqph.fs.quoracdn.net%2Fmain-qimg-2ead6eaace8704c62aaa7ce0372875c3&h=135d41a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://qph.fs.quoracdn.net/main-qimg-645615e369e0cf6df222af196f24de6b\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqph.fs.quoracdn.net%2Fmain-qimg-645615e369e0cf6df222af196f24de6b&h=1de3202d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2f41ebcbff3acb43a7db31c5a9ba2c9931573337","tid":2024694,"uid":193642,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T19:17:25.000Z","msg":"2個大紅燈話俾敵人知自己係邊？"},{"pid":"877a29a967a6655fa76ddff7c7f3aa73585aa9b6","tid":2024694,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T19:24:41.000Z","msg":"酸到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b80cf299da4cd0ff89b9dda9642dfc26160522fa","tid":2024694,"uid":40804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T19:26:06.000Z","msg":"食完weed stoned左再去天安門碌支那豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9669f71d64458dc2737e7d794e84e1c6cd7e15d","tid":2024694,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T20:16:27.000Z","msg":"原來開錯台"},{"pid":"5c605fe3925dbf6ce4eddd8d8314399c9e42181a","tid":2024694,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T20:23:00.000Z","msg":"實戰黎講對紅眼的確唔係優點"},{"pid":"3ba42b81bea8941d34cae7397857c081b11ba901","tid":2024694,"uid":165711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T20:34:05.000Z","msg":"俄佬嘢都敢笑???<br />\n普京：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f2c4b2a53f9d1157d72cb1c3914800c20422aec","tid":2024694,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T20:42:37.000Z","msg":"關你撚事咩"},{"pid":"a2ce554cf9154b108efd52b4e788bc5ca90f9830","tid":2024694,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T20:47:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"739f9f2b7657c0377734ed86db14508c1590e897","tid":2024694,"uid":133387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T21:24:49.000Z","msg":"係「眼紅」俄佬賣俾越南都唔賣俾佢地啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"512cf3efa0c9d2a257dcaeb59e2ae4030e6d3379","tid":2024694,"uid":173271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T21:28:11.000Z","msg":"係show<br />\nshow俾佢睇第日射7佢D軍備"}]}